          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Coronavirus Scammers, Crooks, and Manipulators Act or the SCAM Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases the maximum criminal penalties for mail fraud and wire fraud that occur in connection with the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) national emergency.</p> <p>Additionally, the bill increases the maximum criminal penalties for trafficking in a counterfeit good that is advertised to treat, prevent, or cure COVID-19.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-05-28T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
